#2303
Intersection~
   The sound of hissing rain, pounding hail, and howling wind from outside is
interrupted only by the occasional loud crack of thunder.  Still, this room
seems stable enough for the most part.  Even when the thunder seems to shake the
very ground, not so much as a mote of dust filters down from the ceiling.  The
doors leading into the tor, however, do show signs of weakness, seeming to
tremble with every thunderclap.
